      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOT TORQUE INVEGAS (3) returned in good order with a handy second at Townsville and will have taken a bunch of benefit from that hit-out. Gets a jockey upgrade in the form of Wiggins in the saddle and can go one better against this line-up. TIME TO CRY (5) has been plying her trade in harder south-eastern QLD contests and will appreciate the drop back in company here. Watch for a spike in form. VIKING SUN (6) has placed two from two over this track and trip, gets 2kg off with the claim and draws the inside alley. Ticks a few boxes for a race like this. NOBLE INTENT (1) will be ready to peak now third run back from the break and looks one for the exotics players. SPITZBERG (7) has placed in four of his past five and may earn some minor money again.",
